Premas is proud to launch ORAVAX - a joint venture with Oramed Pharmaceuticals. The venture combines Premas D-Crypt™ technology with Oramed’s POD™ oral delivery of proteins technology to develop a first of its kind Oral #COVID19 #vaccine candidate.
